name: Dot you Limes birthday outfit
description:
A perfect outfit for your little birthday girl! Simple twirl skirt made with pink dots cotton fabric and trimmed with a lime fabric.
Outfit available in a tank top or short sleeve.
Shirt can be customized with any number or letter. 

Please specify tank or short sleeve, shirt size and skirt size at checkout.

Skirt sizes:

12M, 2T, 3T, 4T, 5T 

Each outfit is custom made so please allow 1-2 weeks to receive your order!

xoxo!

name: Graffiti Sneakers
description:
A unique twist on a classic canvas shoe! 
Hand painted with fabric paints and markers. Uniquely personalized for your child!

Canvas Sneakers available in whole sizes only. Please specify boy or girl (styles differ),
child's name and size at checkout.

If you have an art preference, please let me know or I will customize the shoes with my own ideas!

I would also like to give a big thanks to Ashley at Lil Blue Boo for presenting a wonderful idea!

They also make a great gift!

These sneakers are custom made so please allow 1-2 weeks to receive your order!

xoxo

name: Super Burpies set
description:
Super Burpies Cupcake pattern burp cloths.  Appliqued using Gerber pre-washed burp cloths.  Sold as a set.
Perfect gift for a baby shower, birthday or just for your little one!

Each can be personalized with the initial of your choice.  Please submit contact form with custom information.

All pictures are samples of previous orders.

name: Flippin' Fab Flops!
description:
Fabulous ribbon and bow embellished flip flops!  These flip flops are perfect for any warm weather! They are so cute on and so much fun! Each are wrapped in grosgrain ribbon and embellished with boutique style bows. Personalized buttons complete the look! 

Each pair is made unique unless multiples are requested.  

Colors:
Black, White, Lt. Pink, Magenta, Yellow, Green, Blue, Orange, Brown Red, Purple.

Toddler and Adult sizes available.
